				</div>
				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
				
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>These templates that are optimized for remote teaching include step-by-step instructions and links to download each template. We will continue to add new templates to the existing libraries and will add brand new resources as well - so check back often!</p> 
<p><strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1Q1HE3vn2dgQpI69uLZVOTkGGcup8L2D6GDP4GFFizDQ/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">google slide</span>Icon Library<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></strong></p> 
<p><strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1O6_uBwjbY0XEjYFS-l-0SvByVTS0Ua0E707SBs2JsY8/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">google slide</span>Slide Presentation Library<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></strong></p> 
<p><a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1BlP0x7CMQDSrmH3r0UujjSOFjHcWxK6czngDKBfzPiI/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">google slide</span><strong>Google Forms Library</strong><span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link, opens in new window</span></a></p>
